{"word":"ἀπολήγω","slug":"ἀπολήγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπολήγω</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to leave off, desist from</i> a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a> <i>to leave off</i> doing, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:—<a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a> <i>to cease, desist</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}